### 查询记录审计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/audits?type=WEIGHT&recordId={{weightRecordId}}&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 基于删除审计恢复记录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/restore?type=WEIGHT&recordId={{weightRecordId}}&auditId={{deleteAuditId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "changeReason": "undo delete"
}

### 查询恢复后的详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/detail?type=WEIGHT&recordId={{weightRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 基于更新审计回滚记录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/restore?type=WEIGHT&recordId={{weightRecordId}}&auditId={{updateAuditId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "changeReason": "undo update"
}

### 查询回滚后的详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/detail?type=WEIGHT&recordId={{weightRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
